perform mode/graphics mode，fps數可以有4、50（slim版得30）。唔係隻隻驚都有enhance，不過fps穩定啲都好重要。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲天堂我淨係喺嗰度買過驚冇買過機，但平幾百我驚佢有古惑，可能會叫你加多幾百買保養（因為佢隔離嗰間係咁），買機最有保障一定係去藍店，信和有幾間，不過當然而家ps4 到去到後期，平幾百我覺得唔出奇，但都係等其他巴打講下經驗<br />\n<br />\n而家買ps4一定唔遲，傳聞ps5會過多半年公佈，但起碼再等半年以上再發售。當年ps4歐洲出先（好似係），亞洲遲幾個月，之後再炒幾個月，輾轉之下，ps5你起碼2年以後先玩到，所以而家買ps4一定唔遲。"},{"pid":"c8c52edb7d58c03fe2c8f5a2babd5d9b901e36d9","tid":1508064,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:01:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"728545ef90b83e89be61b6aae0d393534fa11dd1","tid":1508064,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09557b21bf90bc7cbf47ddec4903e6660717800e","tid":1508064,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c83e4055387e3870c3f15f7746629b15cec6c3db","tid":1508064,"uid":225364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09557b21bf90bc7cbf47ddec4903e6660717800e","tid":1508064,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:01:39.000Z","msg":"pro 有保 二手嘅市價大概幾多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5e3ab120a026eefbb4c35fec2760dbe8b7e37e","tid":1508064,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76a98349c7c2b3fccb6b07171f6556caa84acd0b","tid":1508064,"uid":182719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"728545ef90b83e89be61b6aae0d393534fa11dd1","tid":1508064,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8c52edb7d58c03fe2c8f5a2babd5d9b901e36d9","tid":1508064,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ed50acf84be22981bf2f559536bfeab9a0862d8","tid":1508064,"uid":225364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:48:20.000Z","msg":"我唔太知啲價錢 但幾成新 買咗幾耐仲有冇保<img s